                        <interp inst="t18430918-name-195" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM GEORGE</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a policeman. I received charge of the prisoner, and found this handkerchief in his trowsers' pocket.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I found it on the ground, put it in my pocket, and when he asked me for a handkerchief, I said I had not got his handkerchief. I did not know it was his.</p>
